      "retrievedDate": "2026-07-01",
      "quotedText": "Hinkson Slough. Season: Second Saturday in February through September 30. Limits \u2014 Daily: 2 trout and 15 warmwater game fish of which not more than 2 may be black bass. Minimum size for trout is 16 inches total length. Minimum size for black bass is 14 inches total length. Possession: 4 trout and 30 warmwater game fish of which not more than 4 may be black bass. Hours: Any hour of the day or night."
